Sitemap generation

Code:

html
<head>
    <title>Best Products | MyStore</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Buy best products online">
    <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "Product",
        "name": "Phone"
    }
    </script>
</head>
